Holmes finished with 22 yards rushing and two touchdowns. Dave Wasinger/Lansing State Journal Fullscreen Buy Photo Michigan State linebacker Riley Bullough tries to stay inbounds as he advances the ball after picking up a fumble in the fourth quarter of the Spartans 30-10 win over the Chippewas at Spartan Stadium, Saturday, September 26, 2015.
